service. ; Photo, The big screen at Harbor Drive-In Theater is blank Sunday 
morning, upstaged by pastor of a Chula Vista church. ; Photo, The congregation 
in the drive-in parking lot wave to the Rev. Veenstra and to each other before 
the start of Easter service. ; Photo, When a church shares a marquee with a 
drive-in theater, the result can sometimes be awkward. VINCE COMPAGNONE / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
