<P>
Doctors said the prognosis was good for a 7-year-old boy who fell through ice 
and was submerged in 40-degree water for nearly 20 minutes on Presque Isle Bay 
near Erie, Pa. Dwayne Peterson, in intensive care at St. Vincent Health Center, 
was fishing with his father when he fell through ice into the bay. He had no 
heartbeat when he was eventually pulled from the bay by John Wronek of the Erie 
