<TEXT>
<P>
Twenty-nine more activists opposed to nuclear weapons were arrested at the 
Nevada Test Site on Easter Sunday, bringing to 283 the number cited during the 
eight-day Lenten Desert Experience. 
</P>
<P>
About 75 demonstrators turned out for a prayer vigil at the main entrance to 
